title: Week 16 Recap: AFC North Madness, NFC East Sadness, and Packers Freeze Titans | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Kevin and Nora dissect a wild Sunday for the AFC North (3:10), pick their Week 16 winners and losers (33:30), run through the Hurry Up (1:15:31), answer listeners' questions (1:17:28), and select their clickbait headlines of the week (1:22:19).

Hosts: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
